{"an5.40:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 5.40 ","an5.40:0.2":"4. Sumanavagga ","an5.40:0.3":"Mahasalaputtasutta ","an5.40:1.1":"â€œHimavantam, bhikkhave, pabbatarajam nissaya mahasala pancahi vaddhihi vaddhanti. ","an5.40:1.2":"Katamahi pancahi? ","an5.40:1.3":"Sakhapattapalasena vaddhanti; ","an5.40:1.4":"tacena vaddhanti; ","an5.40:1.5":"papatikaya vaddhanti; ","an5.40:1.6":"phegguna vaddhanti; ","an5.40:1.7":"sarena vaddhanti. ","an5.40:1.8":"Himavantam, bhikkhave, pabbatarajam nissaya mahasala imahi pancahi vaddhihi vaddhanti. ","an5.40:1.9":"Evamevam kho, bhikkhave, saddham kulaputtam nissaya antojano pancahi vaddhihi vaddhati. ","an5.40:1.10":"Katamahi pancahi? ","an5.40:1.11":"Saddhaya vaddhati; ","an5.40:1.12":"silena vaddhati; ","an5.40:1.13":"sutena vaddhati; ","an5.40:1.14":"cagena vaddhati; ","an5.40:1.15":"pannaya vaddhati. ","an5.40:1.16":"Saddham, bhikkhave, kulaputtam nissaya antojano imahi pancahi vaddhihi vaddhatiti. ","an5.40:2.1":"Yatha hi pabbato selo, ","an5.40:2.2":"arannasmim brahavane; ","an5.40:2.3":"Tam rukkha upanissaya, ","an5.40:2.4":"vaddhante te vanappati. ","an5.40:3.1":"Tatheva silasampannam, ","an5.40:3.2":"Saddham kulaputtam imam; ","an5.40:3.3":"Upanissaya vaddhanti, ","an5.40:3.4":"Puttadara ca bandhava; ","an5.40:3.5":"Amacca natisangha ca, ","an5.40:3.6":"Ye cassa anujivino. ","an5.40:4.1":"Tyassa silavato silam, ","an5.40:4.2":"cagam sucaritani ca; ","an5.40:4.3":"Passamananukubbanti, ","an5.40:4.4":"ye bhavanti vicakkhana. ","an5.40:5.1":"Idha dhammam caritvana, ","an5.40:5.2":"maggam sugatigaminam; ","an5.40:5.3":"Nandino devalokasmim, ","an5.40:5.4":"modanti kamakaminoâ€ti. ","an5.40:5.5":"Dasamam. ","an5.40:5.6":"Sumanavaggo catuttho. ","an5.40:6.0":"Tassuddanam ","an5.40:6.1":"Sumana cundi uggaho, ","an5.40:6.2":"siho dananisamsako; ","an5.40:6.3":"Kalabhojanasaddha ca, ","an5.40:6.4":"puttasalehi te dasati. "}